   <meta property="og:url" content="https://codeximmortal.com/blockchain" />
   <meta property="og:image" content="https://codeximmortal.s3.amazonaws.com/logos/blockchain.png" />
   ```

2. **CDN Integration (via Netlify or Cloudflare)**  
   - Upload `index.html` files to your site  
   - Set up caching for static assets  
   - Use `meta http-equiv="Content-Security-Policy"` for advanced security  

